{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Public inquiry into treatment of people with mental health issues by the DWP",
        "additional_details": "I have experienced appalling treatment from Jobcentre Plus and DWP staff first-hand. This has had a significant and adverse effect on my mental health.\r\n\r\nA public inquiry could review cases involving claimants with mental health issues, and make recommendations for reform to ensure that claimants are treated fairly and appropriately in future.",
        "background": "I want the Department for Work and Pensions to be held to account for its treatment of benefit claimants with mental health issues, many of whom are vulnerable.",
